## Highway Shield Photo Project Most Optimal Routes ##

## Description: 
## This project was created by Ethan S. Hester (TBKS1), I had some code written for me that will parse all waypoint coordinate locations of intersecting highways only and write a script that will plot the most optimal route which intersects every single numbered highway in a selected state, modified for Travel Mapping.

## IMPORTANT -- THIS IS NOT AN OFFICIAL LIST FILE AND SHOULD NOT BE CATEGORIZED AS SUCH ##
## THIS IS STILL IN DEVELOPMENT. ##


